<P>C.I. retains the services of four respected investment counselling firms: <A HREF="fundus.html">BEA Associates</A> of New York, <A HREF="fundasia.html">TCW Asia</A> of Hong Kong, <IMG BORDER=0 ALT="new" SRC="new2.gif"><A HREF="hansbergervalue.html"> Hansberger Global Investors  </A> <IMG BORDER=0 ALT="new" SRC="new2.gif"> of Florida</A> and <A HREF="fundcanada.html">J. Zechner Associates</A> of Toronto.<H3 ALIGN=CENTER>Service to the distribution network and individual clients</H3>A successful investment strategy must be tailored to meet the needs of the individual client. C.I. Funds are available only through brokers, investment dealers, financial planners and other investment professionals. Their understanding of investments and ability to communicate with investors are vital to providing the best possible service.<P>C.I.'s  information-based support materials serve both investors and investment advisers with clear, timely descriptions of current investments and future opportunities.<P><HR><NOFRAMES><CENTER><A HREF="prices.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="Daily Prices" SRC="menu/daily_prices.gif"></A><A HREF="ditip.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="Daily Investment Tip" SRC="menu/daily_tip.gif"></A><A HREF="performance_options.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="Fund Performance" SRC="menu/performance.gif"></A><A HREF="perspective.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="World Report" SRC="menu/world_report.gif"></A><A HREF="managers.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="Funds & Advisers" SRC="menu/funds&advisers.gif"></A><A HREF="managers.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="Hansberger" SRC="menu/hansberger_icon.gif"></A><A HREF="howbuy.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="How To Buy" SRC="menu/how_to_buy.gif"></A><A HREF="cinews.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="What's New" SRC="menu/whats_new.gif"></A><A HREF="directory.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDE