<HTML> <HEAD><TITLE>About C.I. Mutual Funds</TITLE></HEAD> <BODY BGCOLOR="#EBE8DF"><CENTER><TABLE CELLSPACING=2 CELLPADDING=0 BORDER=2><TR><TD><A HREF="home2.html"><IMG BORDER=0 ALT="C.I. Mutual Funds" SRC="pagebanner_white.gif"></A></TD></TR></TABLE></CENTER><P><CENTER><IMG WIDTH=403 HEIGHT=82 BORDER=0 ALT="Investment Questions & Answers" SRC="headings/head_qanda.gif"></A></CENTER><HR NOSHADE><P>On this page, we will try and answer the most common questions that you ask us.  You can give us your suggested questions using our <A HREF="feedback.html">feedback form</A>.  We've started off with a question we are often asked on international investments.<P><HR><P><FONT SIZE=5>Q:</FONT>  Why is diversifiying my investments internationally so important?<P><FONT SIZE=5>A:</FONT>  The fact is, Canadian markets are a relatively small component of the worlds stock and bond market capitalization -- less than 3%.  Restricting your investments to one market means you lose out on the abundant opportunities in the other 97% of markets. In 1995 for example, if you invested only in the Canadian stock market you would have missed the remarkable 30% rise in the U.S. market.  In 1993 the Hong Kong market soared by 100%.  It is impossible to predict when these outstanding rallies will occur, which is why it is essential to maintain ongoing,long-term investments in a wide variety of international markets.<P>Global diversification not only increases the opportunities for growth; it also automatically reduces risk in your portfolio by diluting exposure to the volatility of individual markets and currencies. <P><HR><center><A HREF="home2.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="C.I. Home Page" SRC="menu/about_ci.gif"></A><A HREF="ditip.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="Daily Investment Tip" SRC="menu/daily_tip.gif"></A><A HREF="feedback.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="Feedback to C.I." SRC="menu/feedback.gif"></A><A HREF="prices.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="C.I. Fund Prices" SRC="menu/daily_prices.gif"></A><A HREF="links.html"><IMG WIDTH=115 HEIGHT=49 BORDER=0 ALT="Web Links" SRC="menu/links.gif"></A><P></center><PRE></PRE><FONT SIZE=2>This communication is published by C.I. Mutual Funds Inc. Any commentaries contained in this communication are provided as a general source of information and should not be considered personal investment advice.  Every effort has been made to ensure that the material contained in this communication is accurate at the time of publication.  However, C.I. Mutual Funds Inc. cannot guarantee its accuracy or completeness and accepts no responsibility for any loss arising from any use of or reliance on the information contained herein.<P><A HREF="disclaimer.html">Complete disclaimer text</A><p></FONT>All material on this site is copyright &copy; C.I. Mutual Funds Inc., 1995, 1996<P>Questions?  send mail to <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@cifunds.com">webmaster@cifunds.com</A>.</BODY> </HTML> 
