<h3>The good thing about CSBs!</H3>
We're all disappointed with the mingy interest earned by savings bonds these days.  Yet there is a welcome feature to CSBs this year.  Financial planners and investment dealers have been included in the distribution, which gives planners and advisors another tool for a good financial plan.  CSBs can be one of the many parts of a wisely diversified portfolio.  You diversify to get growth and reduce volatility.  CSBs add a touch of comfort to a plan which should also include the Canadian, U.S., and foreign stock markets, investments in different kinds of industries, and some bonds or balanced funds.  Now, your advisor or planner can help you find the right place for CSBs.  That's how MoneyWorks!<p>
<p>
