<HR SIZE=10><H2><I>Complete Our Beta Testing and Receive FREE Celtics
Tickets</I></H2><HR SIZE=10>

<P>
<IMG SRC="/jpegs/inside_fleet.jpg" WIDTH=500 HEIGHT=150 BORDER=1>
</P></CENTER>
<P><FONT SIZE=+1><FONT SIZE="+2">O</FONT>nce you finish testing our 
super new release of StorageCenter, 
you'll finally have plenty of time to go out and see the
legendary Boston Celtics on the famous parquet floor.  Professional 
basketball never looked better than at the new Fleet Center in Boston! 
Our <B>two seats per game</B> are truly among the best in the house, 
and the view is altogether different. Two rows up from the floor, opposite 
the C's bench, right on the foul line. Hey, they might even lose a basketball 
your way, you're that close! If you've watched on television, or from the 
upper decks or the 'end zones' you'll gain a whole new appreciation for the 
game of professional basketball from these fantastic seats.</FONT></P>

<P><FONT SIZE=+1><FONT SIZE="+2>A</FONT>ll we need is for you to agree to 
complete testing of StorageCenter by the week before the game you pick. 
It'll be easy! We have
a great plan, we walk you through many of the steps, and we're here for
you twenty four hours per day to help. We'll go over the results, collect
all your feedback, and send you the two tickets by Federal Express. You
put your backups on automatic and head for the Fleet Center!</FONT></P>

