<P><A NAME="444"><B>For a limited time, Software Partners is offering a 
special upgrade offer to users of Digital's Storage Library System (SLS)

software:</B></A>
</P>

<UL>
  <LI>SLS users get a free TAPESYS license for each VAX or Alpha CPU running
SLS.</LI>
  <LI>We can convert your SLS database to TAPESYS format for a one time
processing fee.</LI>
  <LI>TAPESYS can read tapes written by SLS.</LI>
  <LI>This offer requires the purchase of a one year maintenance agreement at
our standard rates.</LI> 
  <LI>Software Partners provides 7x24 support.</LI>
  <LI>On site training and consulting available to help optimize your storage
management strategy.</LI>
  <LI>Upgrade offer expires 1/31/97.</LI>
</UL>

<P></P>

<P><B>Advantages of upgrade:</B></P>

<UL>
  <LI>TAPESYS offers field proven features and reliability.  TAPESYS is a
complete solution including backup, restore, and media management.  We have
provided professional storage management for OpenVMS since 1983.</LI>
  <LI>TAPESYS will offer a migration path to unified storage management for
OpenVMS, UNIX, Windows NT, and Windows 95.  This will be achieved by merging <A
HREF="tapesys.html">TAPESYS</A> and <A HREF="StorageCenter.html">
StorageCenter</A> functionality into a single platform providing complete
storage management for distributed computing in 1997.</LI>
  <LI>Software Partners is focused on one thing:  storage management.  So when
you have questions or need support, we can provide answers.</LI>
</UL>
<HR>
<BR>
<CENTER>
<FONT SIZE=-1>Please send comments to
<A HREF="mailto:webmaster@SoftwarePartners.com">webmaster@SoftwarePartners.com
</A><BR>or call us at (508) 887-6409
