<DOCNO>WT17-B23-234</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA027-000287-B045-319</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://bh1.storagecenter.com:80/StorageCenter.html 206.214.152.4 19970114010934 text/html 19159
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
