<DOCHDR>
http://bh1.storagecenter.com:80/tapesys.html 206.214.152.4 19970114011053 text/html 7233
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 01:06:40 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 11-Oct-96 20:34:22 GMT
