<TITLE>Imagemap Error</TITLE><H1>Imagemap Error</H1>Your client did not send any coordinates. Either your client doesn't support imagemap or the map file was not accessed as a map.
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT17-B23-240</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA027-000287-B046-52</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://bh1.storagecenter.com:80/intl_distrib.html 206.214.152.4 19970114011148 text/html 2895
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.1
Date: Tuesday, 14-Jan-97 01:07:35 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 13-Jan-97 21:29:44 GMT
Content-length: 2712
Content-type: text/html
</DOCHDR>
