<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>SafetyPosit from Software Partners</TITLE>
<META NAME="keywords" content="Internet Backup,Telebackup,Connected,
XactLabs,Surefind,Legato,Palindrome">
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#E6E8FA" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<CENTER>
<H1>About SafetyPosit
<BR>from Software Partners</H1>

<P><B><FONT SIZE=5>S</FONT>afetyPosit is a service brought to you by the 
people of Software Partners/32, Inc.  The service provides automatic, 
secure, convenient and reliable data backup from your site over a network 
to a highly secure, professionally managed, state-of-the-art storage system. 
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>B</FONT>ased on our thirteen years of experience in delivering 
industrial strength backup/restore solutions, SafetyPosit combines the power of
large-scale enterprise backup with the ubiquity of the public Internet.
 For small, medium or large operations, this service is a must-have.
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>T</FONT>he uniqueness of our combination is this:  We have the capability to
combine the industry's most robust solution for Intranet backup with the
power of the industry's most thoughtful solution for Internet backup.  In
one GUI, you can manage your onsite backups in the same way as offsite backups,
and achieve total safety. 
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>I</FONT>f all you need are onsite backups, we have StorageCenter.
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>I</FONT>f all you need are offsite backups (too small to have your own tape
drives, tapes and operators?) we have SafetyPosit.
<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>W</FONT>ant to supplement your onsite backups with offsite backups?  Use both,
from Software Partners, today!
</B><BR><BR>
