<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>SafetyPosit(sm) - Repository Security</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#E6E8FA" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<H2><CENTER>SafetyPosit(sm) - Repository Security</CENTER>
</H2> 


<P><FONT SIZE=5>Y</FONT>our data is very safe when deposited in our remote 
secure repository.  In addition to your data being encrypted with RSA 
software, there are various physical security devices employed to ensure your 
files are very secure. Although somewhat general due to our security policy, 
here is a partial inventory of the principle equipment in the SafetyPosit 
facility dedicated to protect your data:
<BR><BR>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=1>
<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100><CENTER><H4>Equipment</H4></CENTER></TD>
<TD><CENTER><H4>Function</H4></CENTER></TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>Concrete Bunker<BR><BR></TD>
<TD>The entire SafetyPosit repository is contained within a windowless 
concrete bunker with a single steel reinforced security door which is 
also tied into the below listed alarm system.<BR></TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>Dedicated Highspeed<BR>Internet Access<BR></TD>
<TD>Currently a T-1 line provides Internet access for the transmitted RSA
encrypted backup files.<BR><BR></TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>IBM firewall<BR><BR></TD>
<TD>Firewall including robust firewall software protects against 
the uninvited.<BR><BR></TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>DEC processor<BR> with RAID<BR></TD>
<TD>64-bit Processor with Redundant Array of Independent Disks protects 
against data loss.<BR></TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>StorageTek<BR>tape library<BR></TD>
<TD>Jukebox further protects against data loss by migrating data 
to DLT tape storage with capacity of 10 terabytes.<BR></TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>Best UPS<BR><BR></TD>
<TD>Uninterruptible &#40;Battery&#41; Power Supply protects against 
potential short term loss of commercial electric power<BR></TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>Kohler 18KW<BR>Generator<BR><BR></TD>
<TD>Natural gas powered electricity supply protects against potential 
longer term loss of commercial power.  The generator is synchronized with 
the UPS as well as the commercial electric source.<BR></TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>Alarm System<BR><BR><BR></TD>
<TD>Protects the data repository from potential break-in.  Also includes 
password required touch-key access system.  Access is logged every 
time the door is open.</TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>Inergen Fire<BR>Suppression<BR>System</TD>
<TD>For quick extinguishing in the event of fire.  The Inergen system consists of three tanks containing Argon, Nitrogen, and Carbon Dioxide.  When blended 
together these gases are not harmful to people, and will not damage equipment 
or data.  The system is also connected to the Alarm System.<BR>
</TD></TR>

<TR>
<TD WIDTH=100>HVAC system<BR><BR></TD>
<TD>Temperature and humidity control provides environmental protection.<BR><BR></TD></TR>
</TABLE>

<BR>
