<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Directions to SP/32</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<BR>
<H3><CENTER><STRONG>Directions to<BR>
Software Partners/32, Inc.<BR>
447 Old Boston Road (Route 1)<BR>
Topsfield, Massachusetts 01983<BR>
Phone: 508-887-6409<BR>
</STRONG></CENTER>
</H3>
<H4><CENTER>
Topsfield Police: 508-887-6533<BR>
Good local mechanic: 508-887-2821<BR>
Sheraton Ferncroft: 508-777-2500<BR> 
Nearest commercial airport is Boston (BOS)<BR>
Our travel agent: Travel Destinations Unlimited 508-887-8441</CENTER>
</H4>
<CENTER>
<HR SIZE="4">
</CENTER>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#1">From The Mass Pike</A> 
<LI><A HREF="#2">From Maine/New Hampshire</A> 
<LI><A HREF="#3">From I-93 (Nashua/Spitbrook et al)</A> 
<LI><A HREF="#4">From Boston</A> 
<LI><A HREF="#5">From Logan Airport</A> 
</UL>
<HR>
<B><A NAME="1">From Mass Pike (Connecticut)</A></B><BR>
<BR>
1. From Mass Pike, go north on Route 128 (also known as I-95)<BR>
<BR>
2. Stay on I-95 as it splits from 128 (follow signs pointing toward 
Maine/New Hampshire)<BR>
<BR>
3. Take Route 1 north off I-95 (Exit 50) toward Topsfield<BR>
<BR>
4. Pass Topsfield Fair Grounds on right<BR>
<BR>
5. Continue through two working traffic lights (1st is Route 97, second
is Ipswich Road, with Turnpike Services
 gas station on your left)<BR>
<BR>
6. Continue about 1/2 mile beyond second light, see our building on right:
single story, 'New Meadows Professional Building', number is '447' on roof,
immediately past Topsfield Veterinary Hospital.<BR>
<HR>
<B><A NAME="2">From Maine/New Hampshire (I-95)</A></B><BR>
<BR>
1. From I-95 in Massachusetts, take exit 54 (Route 133) and proceed east<BR>
<BR>
2. Follow Route 133 to Route 1 (traffic light), turn right on Route 1 (see
Agawam Diner on your right)<BR>
<BR>
3. Proceed about four miles on Route 1, cross into Topsfield (see golf course
on your left)<BR>
<BR>
4. Over a hill, turn left into our parking lot - one-story building, 'New
Meadows Professional Building', with '447' on roof, immediately before Topsfield
Veterinary Hospital.<BR>
<BR>
<HR>
<B><A NAME="3">From I-495 or I-93 (Nashua, etc.)</A></B><BR>
<BR>
From 495 (coming north from direction of Marlboro, I-93, etc.), take Mass
Ave exit (EXIT 43) to North Andover, turn right at bottom of ramp. Go straight,
cross 133 and several other small streets. The N Andover town green will
come up on your right, after 1.6 miles from 495. Proceed straight, the road
divides, bear left near the fire station, which will be on your right, and
onto Salem Street. This is the road to Boxford. Pass the Country Corner
store on your right. Keep on this road for a while, crossing into Boxford.
After about 7.1 miles from 495, you'll come to a Y-intersection, for which
the people coming from your left have a stop sign. You should continue to
the right. The road winds. At a four-way stop, you will cross over Middleton Road. Continue
straight. The road curves to the left, and approaches the Boxford green
on your left. See a flagpole and monument, all on your left.  Careful for
you will come upon a fairly hidden stop sign at the end of the green.<BR>
<BR>
At the stop sign, bear right onto Topsfield Road. In about a mile, cross
over I-95. In another half mile, come into Topsfield. You will see a large
white church on your right, with the Topsfield green on your right also.
At the stop sign, turn left onto Route 97. After about a quarter mile,
take the very next right at a Y intersection onto Ipswich Road.<BR>
<BR>
In a half mile, come to Route 1, with Turnpike Services (filling station) on
your left. Turn left at the stop light onto Route 1 North. Proceed about
1/2 mile to SP/32, in the New Meadows Professional Building on your right
(one-story, white brick building). Come in the left door, up the ramp, see SP/32 on your
left.<BR>
<BR>
<HR>
<B><A NAME="4">From Boston</A></B><BR>
<BR>
1. Take Northeast Expressway out of Boston, follow signs to Tobin Bridge
- Maine/New Hampshire - Route 1 North (If you missed the split left to Route
1 North, continue on I-93 to I-95 north, and get off at I-95 North (the
same as Route 128) toward
Gloucester/Salem, proceed from step 3 in above directions &quot;From Mass
Pike&quot;)<BR>
<BR>
2. Follow Route 1 North through Lynnfield, Saugus and West Peabody. You
will have two opportunities to get onto Route 95, but stay on Route 1. Come
into Topsfield.<BR>
<BR>
3. Pass Topsfield Fair Grounds on right<BR>
<BR>
4. Continue through two working traffic lights. First is Route 97 (BayBank
ATM on right), second is Ipswich Road, with Turnpike Services gas station on your left.<BR>
<BR>
5. Continue about 1/2 mile beyond second light, see our building on right:
single story, white brick front, 'New Meadows Professional Building', number is '447' on roof,
immediately past Topsfield Veterinary Hospital.<BR>
<HR>
<B><A NAME="5">From Logan Airport (BOS)</A></B><BR>
<BR>
1. Out of airport, bear right onto Route 1A - DO NOT GO THROUGH THE 
WILLIAMS TUNNEL and DO NOT GO THROUGH THE CALLAHAN/SUMNER TUNNEL<BR>
<BR>
2. At first rotary, take Route 60 West. Stay on Route 60 to Route 1 North, take
Route 1 North (signs point to Maine/New Hampshire)<BR>
<BR>
3. Follow Route 1 North through Lynnfield, Saugus and West Peabody. You
will have two opportunities to get onto Route 95, but stay on Route 1. Come
into Topsfield.<BR>
<BR>
4. Pass Topsfield Fair Grounds on right<BR>
<BR>
5. Continue through two working traffic lights. First is Route 97 (BayBank
ATM on right), second is Ipswich Road, with Turnpike Services gas station on your left.<BR>
<BR>
6. Continue about 1/2 mile beyond second light, see our building on right:
single story, 'New Meadows Professional Building', number is '447' on roof,
immediately past Topsfield Veterinary Hospital.<BR>
<BR>
