<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>The SafetyPosit Concept</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#E6E8FA" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<CENTER>
<H1>The SafetyPosit Concept</H1>
<P>
<BR>
<I>
<H2>
"Changing the concept of unattended backup by eliminating geographic
 barriers, personnel deployment, security transgressions, and capital outlay,
 for users of mid-range computers, servers and desktops."
</H2>
Capitalizing on our thirteen years experience at delivering industrial-strength
backup/restore software and combining it with the power of the public Internet.
<BR>
</I>
</CENTER>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>S</FONT>afetyPosit provides a much safer alternative to your 
regular backups, which
occur daily, weekly and monthly.  Depending on your communications link
to the outside world, this service can at least supplement your regular
backups, and perhaps even completely replace them.
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>I</FONT>magine being able to set up a schedule 
using a navigable GUI, at your
site, and having backup jobs take off automatically, in the middle of
the night.  These jobs will set up ultra-secure links to a very
sophisticated, professionally operated storage site on the Internet.
Your files will be backed up over that link in a way that is guaranteed
to be immune to prying eyes or breakins.
<P>
<CENTER>
<FONT SIZE=4>THAT'S WHAT SAFETYPOSIT IS ALL ABOUT!  READ ON!<FONT>
</CENTER>
<P><FONT SIZE=5>C</FONT>ustomer files are sent to a secure 
storage facility via the
Internet, frame relay, dedicated lines or direct-dial telephone.
Customers have StorageCenter software installed on their computer 
system to drive the SafetyPosit data transmission process, to look
up files at the storage facility, and to restore the files at their
business or relocation facility when needed.  Successful file transmission
is confirmed by a return message to the customer much like a fax machine
confirms a transmission.
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>D</FONT>ata transmission over the communication 
lines is done using powerful
128-bit encryption algorithms from RSA Data Security, Inc.  Thus your data
is extremely safe, indeed it is safer when backed up via SafetyPosit
than when it is backed up at your own site. The savesets created on
storage media at the storage site are fully encrypted, and can never
be opened by anyone but you (again, RSA's 128-bit private key
cryptosystem is employed).
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>T</FONT>he benefits include instant offsite storage, 
no operator overhead, no
onsite storage equipment (save maintenance costs and capital), and
quick, reliable recovery in the event a file is needed, or in the event
of a complete site disaster.
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>T</FONT>he service includes 24-hour technical 
support and administration to
monitor the service, on-site training, and field service to help customers
with unique needs and requests.
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>I</FONT>dentify strategic files for supplemental 
backup, if your internet access
is limited.  Imagine your precious payroll files backed up nearly 
instantly, extremely securely, and professionally stored, prior to your
regular posting job.  Or how about some complicated database being backed
up weekly, offsite, in addition to whatever you are presently doing. How
would that look to your auditors?
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>S</FONT>afetyPosit is what you need, today, to ensure complete security for your
backups.  Talk to us now to see how you can have SafetyPosit working for
you at your site ... tonight.  
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>T</FONT>omorrow you'll be safer.


<BR><BR>

