<BR>
<CENTER>
<H2>SafetyPosit(sm) Electronic Vaulting Service</H3>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>E</FONT>lectronic vaulting is a new, easy and reliable way to 
backup your irreplaceable computer data.  Electronic vaulting uses advanced 
communications and software to more effectively perform disk backups that 
used to require expensive tape drives and piles of tapes.
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>W</FONT>e all know we should backup up our computer data, but 
most of us have a hard time getting around to it.  SafetyPosit makes it easy 
to start now, before disaster strikes!
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>K</FONT>ey features:<BR><BR>
