<LI><A HREF="fast_and_easy.html">Fast and easy to implement</A></LI></UL></UL>
<BR><BR>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>W</FONT>e would like to tell you more about SafetyPosit.  Let's 
start by answering some Frequently Asked Questions:<BR><BR><UL><UL>
<LI><A HREF="evault_defined.html">What is electronic vaulting?</A></LI><BR><BR>
