<H3>To use the SafetyPosit Slide Show Menu:</H3><BR><BR><B>
<UL>
<LI>Start with the <A HREF="slide_h0001.00.html">first slide</A> and use the
&quot;Next&quot; button on each successive slide to view the entire slide show
sequentially.</LI>  (We recommend this method as a first step) or,<BR><BR>
<LI>Scroll through the <A HREF=#4411>menu</A> below and access the slide of 
