in the VMS and UNIX software marketplace.  MTP drives our marketing, mailing 
and contact systems, and tracks prospects from initial contact through 
invoicing and eventually to permanent technical support.  Every department of 
the Company uses MTP throughout the day to control and report on every aspect 
of prospect/customer contact.<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>D</FONT>irect marketing efforts will include advertising, 
mailing and telephone contact.  Horizontal trade publications which the 
Company has targeted include UNIX Review, Web Week, Info World and Internet 
World.  We'll use an appropriate mix of trade publications, card decks and 
Internet-based advertising, along with direct mail. See the accompanying 
