<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>F</FONT>ollow-up contact and sales efforts will be carried out 
through the Company's in-house sales organization, in parallel with our 
existing software product sales organization.<BR>
<BR>
<H3><CENTER>Additional Sales Channels</CENTER>
</H3>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>W</FONT>e will seek to establish relationships with logical 
partners, enabling them to sell the service to their own customers.<BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>A</FONT>mong the companies with whom we are talking are 
Netscape, Netcom, PSI, UUNET, MFS, etc.<BR>
<BR><CENTER>
