<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Are You An ISP</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#E6E8FA" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<CENTER>
<H2>Are You An ISP?</H2>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>W<FONT>e're looking for you!  
Now, you too can take advantage of the most well thought out strategy for 
day-to-day storage on the public Internet.  <B>SafetyPosit</B> is a service 
that you can offer your end users.  With it, they can supplement
or replace their existing daily backup schemes with safe, secure and reliable
offsite backup services never before available.  They can have their data
offsite in a matter of seconds instead of sending it via CTAM, the old 
fashioned way.  And their data will be ultra secure, since we're the only 
backup/restore software developers who use RSA 128-bit encryption.  They'll need fewer (if any!) tape drives, their
operators will be able to do other, more profitable things, and they'll
be more and more dependent on your extended services over time.<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>Y<FONT>ou can be a reseller, whereby you simply offer 
the service to them and we do the storage here at our site.  Or you 
can be a licensee, whereby you license the software from us, and offer 
storage services on your own, into your own bunker at your site.<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>W<FONT>hichever way you're interested in, we can send you 
reasons why Internet backup is here to stay.  It will greatly enhance 
your business, and will put you in nothing less than a major WIN-WIN 
relationship with your precious customers.<BR>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=5>G<FONT>IVE YOUR PRECIOUS CUSTOMERS A REASON TO STAY WITH 
YOUR SERVICE!  Join the leading ISPs offering this service by having 
your VP of Business Development contact <A HREF="mailto:philj@sp32.com">
Phil Jamieson</A> today.

