<HEAD>
<TITLE> Restore </TITLE>
<H1><CENTER>
<A><IMG SRC="restore.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE HSPACE=4 HEIGHT=75 WIDTH=75></A>
StorageCenter Restore
</CENTER></H1>
<A><CENTER><IMG SRC="Line.Gif"></CENTER></A>
</HEAD>

<BODY>

<BR>
The Restore environment allows you to easily locate and restore files back to disk.  Using the StorageCenter Browsers, you can search for specific files or directories you want to include in the restore operation.  

<P>
If you want to restore files immediately, StorageCenter will automatically create a job for you to restore the files now.  You won't have to spend time creating and scheduling your restore jobs.  When you view the restore work order and job information, StorageCenter displays the date and time the restore ran.

<BR>
<BR>
<H2><CENTER>Restore</CENTER></H2>

<A><CENTER>
<IMG SRC="restorewin.gif" HSPACE=4>
</CENTER></A>

<BR>
<P>
<CENTER>
