<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>StorageCenter Job Calendar</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<CENTER>
<BR>
<H1>
StorageCenter Job Calendar
</H1>
</CENTER>
<A><CENTER><IMG SRC="Line.Gif"></CENTER></A>

<BODY>

<BR>
The StorageCenter Job Calendar tool allows you to easily look up all the jobs that ran and are scheduled to run on a given day.  When you select a specific date, StorageCenter will display all the jobs for that day.  The example below displays all the jobs scheduled for February 23, 1996.

<BR>
<BR>
<A><CENTER>
<IMG SRC="calendar.gif" HSPACE=4>
</CENTER></A>

<BR>
<P>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="conclusion.html">Continue the StorageCenter demo<IMG SRC="arrow.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE HSPACE=4></A>
</CENTER>

