<HEAD>
<TITLE>SafetyPosit(sm) eliminate special hardware needs</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#E6E8FA" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<BR>
<CENTER>
<H2>SafetyPosit(sm) Eliminates the Need for Special Hardware</H2>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>T</FONT>he most common method of backing up data on hard disks 
is to use a tape drive. For small organizations this may mean a single tape 
drive.  Since most inexpensive drives have limited capacity, it may be 
necessary to manually change tapes during business hours to perform a 
complete backup.  Larger organizations may invest in a tape autochanger or 
tape library which automatically change tapes.  While this adds convenience, 
it also adds expense.
</P><P>
<FONT SIZE=5>W</FONT>hether you are talking about a small tape drive or a 
large tape library, one thing holds true....whatever you buy today will be 
too small or too slow a year from now.  Disk drives are growing so fast that 
its difficult for tape drives to keep up.</P>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>S</FONT>afetyPosit offers an alternative to investing in rapidly 
depreciating, single purpose hardware.  SafetyPosit takes advantage of the 
Internet access you already have or gives you added justification to invest 
in the communications solution you really need.</P>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>W</FONT>ith SafetyPosit there is no need to purchase single 
purpose hardware or software.  You provide access to the Internet and we 
provide the rest!
</P>
<BR><BR>
