<CENTER>
<H2>Fast and Easy to Implement</H3>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<P><FONT SIZE=5>W</FONT>ith SafetyPosit we provide software that enables you 
to send backups to our secure off-site storage vault. Our software features 
an easy to use graphical user interface.  You can download and install our 
software in less than an hour.  You can start doing secure off-site backups 
today!  And if you ever have a problem, our technical support staff is only a 
phone call away.</P>

<P><FONT SIZE=5>W</FONT>ith conventional backup methods you may have to shop 
for a tape system, shop for backup software, and shop for an off-site storage 
service.  Once you get your hardware and software you may have to spend hours 
or days struggling with hardware driver configuration and other bothersome 
installation problems.
</P>

