<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Who Can Use SafetyPosit(sm)?</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#E6E8FA" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<BR>
<CENTER>
<H2>Who Can Use SafetyPosit(sm)</H2>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>S</FONT>afetyPosit is designed to meet the needs of a wide 
spectrum of computer users. These range from small office or home office 
users, to small businesses and departments within large organizations, to 
large corporate data centers.  SafetyPosit is not a one size fits all 
solution, but rather a flexible service offering that can be tailored to meet 
your needs.  Please select what best describes your situation so we describe 
how SafetyPosit can help:<BR><BR>
<UL><UL>
<LI><A HREF="home_user.html">Home user   (available Q3 '96)</A></LI><BR><BR>
<LI><A HREF="profess_user.html">Professional office</A></LI><BR><BR>
<LI><A HREF="small_user.html">Small business</A></LI><BR><BR>
<LI><A HREF="dept_reg_user.html">Department or Regional Office</A></LI><BR><BR>
<LI><A HREF="corp_user.html">Corporate Data Center</A></LI><BR><BR>
</UL></UL>
</P>
<BR><BR>
<HR>
<BR><BR>
