<HEAD>
<TITLE>SafetyPosit(sm) Is Secure</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#E6E8FA" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<BR>
<CENTER>
<H2>Will my data be secure?</H2>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>O</FONT>ne of the advantages of SafetyPosit is that we are able 
to provide an extremely secure storage environment regardless of how much 
data you have to back up.  We have taken many steps to ensure the security of 
SafetyPosit.  First, <A HREF="/SafetyPosit/SP_secure.html">our secure storage 
site</A> includes a windowless concrete bunker with controlled access and 
advanced security alarm and fire suppression system.  We are protected from 
electrical power interruptions by an Uninterruptible Power Supply (UPS) and a 
natural gas powered, 18 KW backup generator.
</P>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>I</FONT>n additional to these physical and environmental 
protections, we have incorporated the most advanced data security software 
available.  We of course have an Internet firewall to prevent unauthorized 
access.  In addition, we have incorporated advanced encryption and node 
authentication software from RSA Data Security, the recognized technology 
leader in commercial data security.
</P>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>A</FONT>ll data transmitted is <A HREF="primer.html #6">encrypted
</A> with a 128 bit key.  This ensures that no one else can read your data.  
In addition, SafetyPosit uses <A HREF="primer.html #6.1">node authentication
</A> to prevent impostors from gaining access to SafetyPosit.  Node 
authentication uses RSA's digital signature consisting of a 1024 digit 
public/private key system.</P>

<CENTER>
