<HEAD>
<TITLE>How Can SafetyPosit Be Obtained?</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#E6E8FA" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000">


<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<CENTER><H1>How Can SafetyPosit Be Obtained?</H1></CENTER>

<P>
<FONT SIZE=5>S<FONT>afetyPosit is primarily offered through Internet Service
Providers (ISPs) and Off-site Storage Providers (OSPs) as either <A HREF=
"resellerprog.html">resellers</A> or <A HREF="licenseeprog.html">licensees</A>.
A SafetyPosit Reseller markets SafetyPosit to its client base but relies on
Software Partners to actually receive backups and operate the storage vault.  A
SafetyPosit Licensee operates its own storage vault using software, policies,
and procedures licensed from Software partners.
<BR><BR>
<HR>
<BR><BR>
