<H2><CENTER>Device</CENTER></H2>

You will need to define a device (tape drive) that StorageCenter can use for writing information to and reading information from tape. The device and its device special file information allow StorageCenter to communicate with the device.  You can view all the devices defined in the database on the Device window.  

