<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>SafetyPosit(sm) for Home Users</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#E6E8FA" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#FF0000">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/logo_and_tagline.gif">
<IMG SRC="/gifs/Line.gif" WIDTH=100%>
<BR>
<CENTER>
<H2>SafetyPosit(sm) for Home Users</H2>
</CENTER>
<BR>
<P>
<B>Problem</B>:  Home PCs are frequently used to store invaluable personal 
information.  This may include checkbook registers, tax returns, addresses 
and recipes, job search information, and school projects.  In addition to 
data files, there may be shareware that you've spent years collecting from 
bulletin boards.  Many computers come preloaded with valuable software on the 
hard drive but don't include the original diskettes.  
Finally, there are important configuration and
system files.  What do all of these types of data have in common?  They all
would be very hard to replace if your PC were stolen or destroyed in a fire.
And what about a hard drive crash?  Ask some long time PC users and they'll 
tell you that sooner or later you may experience a hard drive failure.  
Later may not be better than sooner since you'll have more irreplaceable 
data by then.  Most home PCs don't have a practical way to backup the hard 
drive since using 3.5" diskettes for large amounts of data is impractical.
</P>
<P>
<B>Solution</B>:  
rather than investing in limited use hardware like a tape drive, take
advantage of the on-line communications you already have.  SafetyPosit allows
you to send your files to our storage vault for safe keeping.  If you ever 
need to restore a lost file, SafetyPosit can download it in a few minutes.  
You can do this from anywhere in the world!  Because SafetyPosit <A HREF=
"primer.html #6">encrypts</A> your files before they leave your PC, you 
maintain complete privacy.  You will have the only valid <A HREF=
"primer.html #6">encryption key</A> and no one else can read your data.  
With SafetyPosit, you will be able to do an initial <A HREF="primer.html #1">
full backup</A> and then refresh this with periodic <A HREF="primer.html #3">
incremental backups</A> and <A HREF="primer.html #5">consolidation backups
</A>.</P>
<P>
<B>System and Network Requirements</B>:  to be announced</P>
<P>
<B>Communications Options</B>:  to be announced</P>
<P>
<B>Pricing</B>:  to be announced</P>
<P>
<B>Register</B>:  SafetyPosit is not available for Windows 3.1, Windows 95, 
or MAC OS at this time.  Windows 95 will be supported in mid-1997.  
If you would like 
to be notified when SafetyPosit is available for any these operating systems 
or if you would like to be considered for Beta Testing (user validation 
testing), please <A HREF="/SafetyPosit/sp_register.html">register</A>.
</P>
<BR><BR>
<HR>
<BR><BR>
<B>
