Hungary's Dunaferr Borrows $25M From S. Korea Eximbank
AP-Dow Jones News Service

A del-koreai Eximbank 25 000 000 $-t kolcsonoz a magyar allami tulajdonu
Dunaferr Rt-nek. A kolcson visszafizetesi ideje 20 ev, 5 evig nincs fizetes,
a kamat 3-4% !!!
A kolcson resze az 50 000 000 $-os del-koreai kormanykolcsonnek
Magyarorszag reszere.

=REGIONALIS HIREK

UKRAINIANS BUY DOLLARS AS PANIC BREAKS OUT OVER NEW CURRENCY. The
government's announcement that it will introduce a new currency on 2
September has triggered massive panic-selling of karbovantsi by
Ukrainians, Western agencies reported on 26 August. The karbovanets, the
country's transitional tender, was trading at between 220,000 and
300,000 to $1 at various exchange points throughout the country,
significantly higher than the official bank rate on 16 August of 176,100
karbovantsi/$. Meanwhile, the Socialist caucus has complained that the
planned exchange rate of 100,000 karbovantsi to 1 hryvna will undervalue
the new currency and cheat the Ukrainian people. - Chrystyna Lapychak

NORDIC COUNTRIES NOT TO GIVE BALTS SECURITY GUARANTEES. The prime
ministers of Finland, Sweden, Norway, Denmark, and Iceland, meeting in
Helsinki on 26 August, decided that their countries cannot give the
Baltic States any guarantees for their security, BNS reported. The
premiers however, expressed the hope that the situation in the Baltics
becomes stable and that the three states will be granted EU membership.
Finnish Prime Minister Paavo Liopponen said his country will continue
defense cooperation with Estonia, but he noted that this did not qualify
as "far-reaching military cooperation." The premiers will invite their
Baltic counterparts to the next Nordic Council of Ministers' meeting in
Copenhagen in November. They also decided to allocate 100 million ECUs
($128 million) for environmental projects due to be launched in the
Baltic region next year. - Saulius Girnius

SLOVAK PREMIER DISCUSSES PROPOSED CABINET CHANGES WITH PRESIDENT.
Vladimir Meciar on 26 August met with Michal Kovac to discuss the
proposed cabinet reshuffle, Slovak media reported. Kovac, who has the
constitutional right to appoint and dismiss cabinet members, is reported
to have responded positively to the personnel changes. The meeting
between Meciar and Kovac, who have been feuding for three years, was the
first since the visit of Pope John Paul II to Slovakia in June-July last
year. Following their talks, the political council of Meciar's Movement
for a Democratic Slovakia met to discuss the cabinet changes. TASR
reported on 27 August that the three ministers to be dismissed are
Foreign Minister Juraj Schenk, Economy Minister Jan Ducky, and Interior
Minister Ludovit Hudek. - Sharon Fisher

ANOTHER BOMB IN BRATISLAVA KILLS POLICEMAN. An off-duty policeman died
early on 26 August of injuries sustained in a bomb explosion at a money
exchange booth outside the Kmart department store in central Bratislava,
Slovak and international media reported. The 26 year-old policeman died
in the hospital. Police said the explosion was not related to the bomb
attack of the previous day (see OMRI Daily Digest, 26 August 1996). The
owner of the exchange booth said that his office had been set on fire
earlier this summer. - Sharon Fisher

ROMANIA'S ETHNIC HUNGARIAN LEADERS MEET WITH HUNGARIAN PREMIER.
Representatives of ethnic Hungarians from Romania, meeting with Gyula
Horn in Budapest on 26 August, urged that negotiations on the Hungarian-
Romanian draft basic treaty be reopened, Hungarian media reported. They
argued that Budapest had acted under considerable international pressure
and had neglected the interests of Romania's 1.6 million ethnic
Hungarians. But Ferenc Somogyi, state secretary at the Hungarian Foreign
Ministry, insisted that the expectations of the international community
"coincided with our own interests." The Democratic Alliance of
Hungarians in Romania claimed that the draft treaty fails to regulate
the restitution of confiscated Church assets and that it is unclear on
the minorities' right to education in Hungarian. - Zsofia Szilagyi

[ Me'g a bosnyakok is szavazhatnak kulfoldrol !!!

 Mi magyarok me'g mindig nem!!! ]

HUNGARY'S BOSNIAN REFUGEES CAST THEIR BALLOTS. Some 2,000 Bosnian
refugees in Hungary have voted in the Bosnian national elections, ahead
of hundreds of thousands of others still living in exile, Reuters
reported on 26 August. According to an OSCE official the voting was
completed without any irregularities among Hungary's Muslim-dominated
Bosnian community. Under the Dayton agreement, Bosnian citizens living
abroad are entitled to vote for parliamentary and local council
candidates prior to the Bosnian elections, which are set for 14
September. - Zsofia Szilagyi

ALBANIA PRAYS FOR MOTHER TERESA. Albanian President Sali Berisha has
said his country is praying for Nobel Peace Prize laureate Mother
Teresa, Reuters reported on 26 August. The world famous missionary, who
was born Agnes Gonxhe Bojaxhiu to Albanian parents in Skopje, marks her
86th birthday on 27 August. Berisha said in a telegram that Albanians
"unite in prayer and hope for your quick recovery and full health so you
may continue your humane and divine mission." Mother Teresa was
hospitalized on 20 August and diagnosed with malaria, a chest infection,
and an irregular heart beat. Her Missionaries of Charity opened a branch
in Tirana following the end of communism. - Fabian Schmidt

POSTPONING THE INEVITABLE?

 The OSCE commission monitoring the 14 September elections in
Bosnia-Herzegovina announced today that the municipal part of the ballot
will be postponed to April or May of next year. This comes in response
to evidence that massive pressure and coercion have been used on Bosnian
Serbs in the Republika Srpska (RS) and especially in Serbia to register
to vote in key towns that had large Muslim populations before the war
but are now mainly Serb. While the postponement seems to extricate the
OSCE from a series of difficulties for the moment, it potentially opens
up a Pandora's box of new ones.

 The UNHCR yesterday was but the latest body to point out that the
Serbs are using registration to consolidate the ethnic partition of the
country, Oslobodjenje wrote this morning. It appears that up to 100,000
Bosnian Serb refugees have been "encouraged" to sign up to vote in towns
like Srebrenica, Brcko, or Bijeljina at the risk of losing their
humanitarian aid rations or of facing other unpleasant consequences. The
governing Serbian Democratic Party (SDS) did this in keeping with its
aim of preventing Muslims or Croats from reestablishing a foothold in
areas from which they have been "ethnically cleansed." It also wants to
bring all Bosnian Serbs into the RS as a prelude to realizing the
party's frequently stated goal of a greater Serbia.

 The Serbs have not been alone in resorting to such electoral
engineering. The Muslim Party of Democratic Action (SDA) has urged
refugees from Srebrenica and other eastern Bosnian towns to vote in the
formerly Serb-held suburbs of Sarajevo. Among the Croats, moreover,
there is ample evidence that the governing Croatian Democratic Community
(HDZ) has been encouraging its people to resettle and register in areas
that form a compact whole and border Croatia.

 What made the Serbs' actions stand out, however, was their
magnitude and systematic nature. The SDS was able to do this because of
one of the many contradictions inherent in the Dayton agreement. On the
one hand, that document guarantees the right of refugees to go home and
the right to freedom of movement in a multi-ethnic Republic of Bosnia
and Herzegovina. Thanks to these principles, refugees may fill out the
so-called P-1 form that enables them to vote in the place where they
registered for the 1991 census, i.e. in their home area before they were
ethnically cleansed. On the other hand, the treaty also allows people to
register with the P-2 form, which permits them to cast their ballot in
the place where they currently live or for a place where they intend to
live in the future. It is this last point that the Serbs have apparently
abused the most by recruiting large numbers of refugees in Serbia to
claim that they intend to move to places like Srebrenica and hence ask
to be allowed to vote in that town's municipal election.

 OSCE election supervisor Robert Frowick's decision today, however,
may raise more problems than it solves. The municipal vote may have been
put off until next spring, but six additional levels of elections are
still slated for 14 September. Will these be at all affected by the
registration imbroglio? Will the OSCE be able to save most of the
electoral process by sacrificing part of it, or will the whole thing
collapse? When the municipal ballot finally does take place, how will
voters be allowed to register? Will the international community in the
meantime finally get serious about enforcing freedom of movement and
other basic Dayton principles, or will it continue the inaction and
waffling that invite abuse in the this part of the world?

 And how will the parties react to the OSCE's announcement? The
postponement probably means that the SDA will call off its threat to
boycott the 14 September vote, but might not the SDS now launch its own
boycott, since its leaders have repeatedly said that all levels of the
elections must take place on time? This point was reaffirmed only
yesterday by the acting SDS chief, Aleksa Buha, Nasa Borba wrote this
morning. One might also ask what the entire affair says about the role
in the Bosnian peace process of Serbia and its president, Slobodan
Milosevic, on whose territory much of the wholesale coercion took place.

And all this still leaves the question of who will organize, supervise,
and provide security for the 1997 round. Most of the international
presence in Bosnia-Herzegovina specified by the Dayton agreement is
slated to wind up at the end of 1996, if not sooner. U.S. President Bill
Clinton in particular seems opposed to any continuation of IFOR after
that date.

Will the international community "declare victory and withdraw" (to
borrow the phrase from the Vietnam War) after the September vote - and
allow the three nationalist parties to run the 1997 elections? If so,
why bother postponing the inevitable at all? - Patrick Moore

"OPERATION VOLCANO" BRINGS VOCAL SERBIAN RESPONSE. But NATO's best-known
activities this past week centered on its destruction of previously
unreported Bosnian Serb arms. IFOR continued Operation Volcano, which
dealt with the weapons cache found in Margetici two weeks earlier (see
OMRI Special Report, 20 August 1996). According to Onasa reports, IFOR
that day destroyed 36 tons of anti-tank and anti-personnel mines and
other munitions in pits 27 meters wide and 7 meters deep. This was
accompanied by Bosnian Serb protests against the IFOR operation.
Plavsic, complaining that the arms are being destroyed at the same time
as the Muslims and Croats in the Bosnian federation are being armed,
proposed that IFOR instead sell the weapons or transfer the depot, AFP
reported. As part of an aggressive media campaign, the Pale-based news
agency SRNA alleged that the detonations have caused cracks in the walls
of "the region's oldest church." Bosnian Serb officials' litany of
complaints against Operation Volcano also includes allegations that the
operation is jeopardizing underground water supplies and that IFOR has
been dumping radioactive waste materials. Responding to the allegations,
IFOR spokesman Maj. Max Marriner has said water sources are in no danger
and IFOR is "not in the business of dumping radioactive waste," Onasa
reported. In any event, Operation Volcano ended on 24 August. - Stan
Markotich and Daria Sito Sucic

WHAT WILL BE DONE WITH ALL THE BOSNIAN SERB MUNITIONS? Questions have
nonetheless arisen over what to do about an additional 16 sites declared
by the Bosnian Serbs. Reportedly ten of those cites contain some 2,600
tons of munitions similar to those discovered at Margetici. Suggesting
that the additional munitions deposits may not be destroyed, Maj. Brett
Boudreau has said that "all options are under consideration," Reuters
reported on 21 August. Some speculation already centers on the
possibility that IFOR may allow the Bosnian Serbs "to move the
contraband to an already approved storage site," Reuters added. - Stan
Markotich

IFOR STEPS UP CONTROL IN BRCKO REGION. Still in the Republika Srpska,
IFOR troops have increased their control over goods and passengers and
set up new checkpoints around the northern Bosnian town of Brcko, Onasa
reported on 19 August. Brcko is becoming an increasingly important issue
for both the Bosnian Serbs and the Muslim-Croat federation. While
Bosnian Serb leaders have said that "Brcko is more important for Serbs
than peace," Bosnian federation officials and parties also underscore
its significance for their side. The status of Brcko is to be decided by
14 December through arbitration, as specified in the Dayton agreement.
The Brcko corridor is the only traffic artery connecting Bosnian Serbs
in western parts of the country with those in eastern areas and with
Serbia. Bosnian federation Vice President Ejup Ganic stressed that 56
percent of Brcko's prewar population was Muslim and that those forcibly
expelled by Serbs should return to their homes. Ganic said the subject
of arbitration is the whole area, including the town itself, and not
just the contentious line of separation around the town, as Serbs claim.
- Daria Sito Sucic

=SAJTOSZEMLE

Belpolitika

Horn Gyula miniszterelnok Karl Imret jelolte ki tegnap az
energiaar-emelesi javaslat felulvizsgalatat vegzo kormanymegbizotti
tisztsegre. Az MSZP parlamenti kepviselojenek, egyben az Orszaggyules
gazdasagi bizottsaga alelnokenek napokon belul fel kell allitania az
arfelulvizsgalo bizottsagot. A feladat: masfel-ket honapnyi elemzes
utan tovabb kell faragni a kormany altal elutasitott aremelesi
javaslaton. Hirek szerint a kormany sokallja a Magyar Energia Hivatal
30 szazalekot is elero javaslatait, es legfeljebb 25-26 szazalekos
emelest tart indokoltnak. Szabo Imre, a MEH foigazgatoja allitja: az
orszag legjobb szakembereivel dolgoztak, es nem kepviseltek elfogultan
az energiaipar erdekeit. Szerinte a kormany dontese, miszerint
oktoberrol januarra halasztotta az energia aranak emeleset, nem tett
jot a hivatalnak, de elismeri, hogy a kabinetnek a szuk szakmai
indokokon felul mas tenyezoket is figyelembe kell vennie. Simonyi
Tamas, a Bank Austria Girocredit magyarorszagi igazgatoja ugy veli: a
kormany ezuttal elobbre sorolta a politikai megfontolasokat a kulfoldi
befektetok erdekeinel es ez visszauthet. Januarban meg nagyobb
aranyban kell majd emelni az arakat, hogy teljesithessek a vallalt
garanciakat (Nepszabadsag: Az energiahivatal...1.o., Magyar Hirlap:
Karl Imre...1.,3.o.).

Pongracz Tibor, az elozo kabinet privatizacios allamtitkara az Uj
Magyarorszagnak (Titkos...1.,7.o.) elmondta: nem lehet tisztan latni
az energiaar-emeles elhalasztasanak kovetkezmenyeit, mert az
energiaprivatizacio titkos szerzodesek alapjan folyt, s az uggyel
kapcsolatos tajekoztatassal meg ados a kormany.

Pongracz szerint az sem lehetetlen, hogy a koltsegvetes terhere kell
majd megfizetni azt a nyolcszazalekos hasznot, amelytol most elestek a
befektetok. Velemenye szerint az energiaprivatizacio "sikertortenete"
immar botranyos, s nagy kerdes, milyen kovetkezmenyekkel jar, ha a
kormany nem teljesiti vallalt kotelezettsegeit.

Vastagh Pal igazsagugy-miniszter vezetesevel hetfon ulest tartott az
MSZP-frakcio alkotmanyozassal foglalkozo ottagu munkacsoportja. A tobb
mint haromoras tanacskozast kovetoen a miniszter elmondta: egyertelmu
volt a bizottsag allasfoglalasa abban, hogy az alkotmanyozast folytani
kell, es ezt a javaslatot terjesztik kedden az MSZP tanacskozo szervei
ele. Bihari Mihaly, az Orszaggyules alkotmanyugyi bizottsaganak
alelnoke kozolte: allasfoglalasuk szerint az alkotmanykoncepcioba
bekerulhet a szocialis allam, az erdekegyeztetes fogalma
(Nepszabadsag: A szocialistak...4.o.).

Kuncze Gabor belugyminiszter szeptember elsejei hatallyal felmentette
megbizatasa alol Nyiri Sandort, a miniszterium rendeszeti helyettes
allamtitkarat. Ezzel egyidoben felmentette az ORFK bunugyi foigazgatoi
beosztasa alol Kacziba Antalt es kinevezte a tarca rendeszeti
helyettes allamtitkarava. Lapinformaciok szerint Kacziba tabornok
feladatkoret az uj foigazgato kinevezeseig Kiss Erno ezredes, az ORFK
gazdasagvedelmi foosztalyvezetoje veszi majd at. A lapok beszamoloi
szerint Kuncze Gabor hetfon tobb oran at targyalt Pinter Sandor
orszagos rendorfokapitannyal Kacziba Antal tavozasa es az uj
rendorsegi szervezet, a Kozponti Bunuldozesi Igazgatosag letrehozasa
utani teendokrol. Belugyi korokbol ellentmondasos hirek keringenek
arrol, szoba kerult-e a talalkozon a KBI vezetojenek
szemelye. Allitolag Kuncze mar a mai sajtotajekoztaton bejelenti, hogy
kit nevez ki a feketegazdasag elleni hatekony fellepes erdekeben
letrehozando szervezet elere. Masok szerint erre csak a het masodik
feleben kerul sor (Nepszabadsag: BM... 4.o.). A Magyar Hirlap (Ki
lesz... 4.o.) megjegyzi: ugy latszik a rendorsegnel uralkodo - egyes
velemenyek szerint szakmai-moralis valsag miatt - egyertelmuen Nyiri
Sandort teszik felelosse, mikozben a altala iranyitott rendeszeti
foosztaly csupan a miniszter velemenyezo, dontes-elokeszito szervekent
mukodik, s a hatalyos jogszabalyok szerint utasitasadasi joga is
kizarolag Kunczenak van.

Az ORFK vezetoje altal, az 1994 julius 14-en az Alkaloidaban
megsemmisitett, illetve visszaalakitott kabitoszer ugyeben elrendelt
vizsgalat elso resze befejezodott. Eszerint a megsemmisites
elrendeleseben rendori szerv nem vett reszt. A rendorseg szerepe ebben
az ugyben annyi volt, hogy a kabitoszernek az Alkaloidaba torteno
szallitasat biztositotta. Az ugy tovabbi reszleteinek feltarasa es az
esetleges szemelyi felelosseg megallapitasa erdekeben a vizsgalatot
tovabb folytatja az ORFK (Nepszabadsag: Hirek... 15.o.).

Az Uj Magyarorszagnak (Hataskor nelkuli... 1.,4.) Konya Imre, volt
belugyminiszter elmondta: miniszterkent nem volt infomracioja az
eljarasrol, mert az ilyen jellegu ugyek, tehat, hogy kabitoszert
gyogyszerre alakithassanak at, nem kerulnek miniszteri
szintre. Torvenytelenseg eseten azonban mar kormanyzati felelosseg a
vizsgalodas, most ennek lehetunk tanui. Mivel az esetre az o
kormanyzasuk utolso napjan kerult sor, ertelemszeruen nem tarhattak
fel a torvenytelenseget.

Magyarorszagon evente tobb mint tizezer szemelygepkocsit lopnak el.
Tobbseget hamis okmanyokkal kulfoldre szallitjak, illetve a
feketepiacokon ertekesitik. A rendorseg eddig meg nem talalta meg az
egyre terjeszkedo szervezett autotolvajbandak felderitesenek hatekony
modszeret. Ennek lehetosegeirol targyalt Budapesten 16 orszag
szakembere a tegnap kezdodott haromnapos nemzetkozi konferencian.
Pinter Sandor, az ORFK vezetoje szerint iden az huszezret is elerheti
a lopott autok szama, ami ismet rekord lesz. A gepkocsilopasok
mennyisege harom eve megallithatatlanul novekszik. A fokapitany
szerint indokolt lenne Europaban szabvanyositani a gepjarmuvek
forgalmi engedelyet. Megkonnyitene a bunuldozo hatosagok munkajat, ha
valamennyi rendorseg azonos szempontok alapjan intezkedne a lopott
gepkocsik korozeserol, es ha egyseges nemzetkozi nyilvantartast
vezetnenek valamennyi, Europaban ellopott szemelygepkocsirol
(Nepszabadsag: Egyseges... 15.o., Magyar Nemzet:
Magyarorszag... 1.,4.).

A gyermekek es fiatalok szexualis kizsakmanyolasa elleni kuzdelem elso
izben lesz nagy nemzetkozi tanacskozas targya a ma Stokholmban kezdodo
vilagkongresszuson. Az UNICEF jelentese szerint jelenleg egymillio
gyermeket kenyszeritenek prostituciora a vilagban, az igy kitermelt
jovedelmek dollarban milliardos nagysagrenduek. Garamvolgyi Laszlo, az
ORFK szovivoje cafolja, hogy Magyarorszag lenne az europai
gyermekprostitucio egyik legfontosabb beszerzesi forrasa
(Vilaggazdasag: Gyermekprostitualtak... 1.,6., Nepszabadsag:
Nemzetkozi... Gyermekprostitucio... 15.o.).

Eddig tobb mint hetvenezer alairas gyult ossze a szukseges szazezerbol
1994 ota annak erdekeben, hogy az Orszaggyules irjon ki nepszavazast a
halalbuntetes visszaallitasarol - nyilatkozta a Nepszabadsagnak
(Hetvenezer... 4.o.) Toth Tamas, a Fejer megyei Sarszentmihaly
polgarmestere, akinek a fiat negy evvel ezelott kegyetlenul
meggyilkoltak es az egyik kezdemenyezoje volt az alairasgyujtestnek.
Toth szerint belathato idon belul osszegyulik a szazezer alairas.

A kozszolgalati televizio nem hajlando musoridot biztositani Magyar
Jozsef nagyszabasu, fesztivaldijat is nyert
dokumentumfilm-sorozatanak, a "Mi forradalmunk" cimu otreszes
alkotasnak, s mereven elzarkoztak attol, hogy a "lebilincselo
filmalkotast megismerhesse a magyar tarsadalom".
(Magyar Nemzet: Hirek... 4.o.).

A Nepszava (Sorozatos... 1.,4.) kozli az Allami Szamvevoszek most
elkeszult jelenteset, amely szerint a Magyarok Vilagszovetsege
1993-1995-ben 661,6 millio forint bevetellel rendelkezett, amelybol
580 millio forint szarmazott az allami koltsegvetesbol. Az ASZ szerint
az MVSZ "szabadon" gazdalkodhatott, leven a felhasznalasi celokat a
koltsegvetesi torveny es a Miniszterelnoki Hivatal egyetlen evben sem
hatarozta meg. A vizsgalat sorozatos konyvelesi hibakat fedezett fel
az MVSZ-nel. Csoori Sandor, az MVSZ elnoke az ASZ eszreveteleit
levelben koszonte meg, kifejtve: "a tajekoztatoban felsorolt
megjegyzeseket tudomasul vesszuk".

Az FKGP vezetese a het vegen haromnapos zartkoru tanacskozast tart egy
meg nem nevezett videki helyszinen. A rendezveny alkalmaval
megvitatjak a part elnoke altal, Kisgazda ut cimmel elkeszitett uj
valasztasi strategiai elkepzeleseket. Az Uj Magyarorszagban
(Titkos... 4.o.) Torgyan Jozsef partelnok elmondta: minimalis tervuk,
hogy megotszorozzek jelenlegi mandatumaik szamat, termeszetesen a
jelenlegi valasztasi struktura mellett. A jovore vonatkozo
elkepzeleseit egyelore hetpecsetes titokkent orzik.

Gazdasag

A Magyar Hirlapnak (IMF-dontes... 3.o.) Mark Allen, a Nemzetkozi
Valutaalap magyarorszagi kepviseloje elmondta: aggaszto, hogy a
tb-alapok hianya joval meghaladja a tervezettet, de remelik, hogy a
kozponti koltsegvetes kedvezo helyzete ezt ellensulyozni fogja. Az IMF
igazgatotanacsa szerdan vitatja meg a keszenleti hitelmegallapodashoz
kapcsolodo felulvizsgalat eredmenyeit es dont arrol, hogy Magyarorszag
szamara tovabbra is hozzaferheto-e a hitelkeret.

A Nepszabadsag (ASZ-vizsgalat... 1.,8.) kozli: a kozep-europai terseg
eddigi legnagyobb privatizacioja, a 67 szazalekban kulfoldi
magantulajdonba kerult Matav tulajdonosvaltasa, az Allami Szamvevoszek
vizsgalata szerint koncepciotlan es szabalytalan. Az 1993-as, elso
privatizacios utemben a kisebbsegi tulajdonos teljes koru tulajdonosi
jogositvanyokat szerzett, es az allam a bevetel felet visszaforgatta a
tarsasagba. Az 1995. vegi, masodik utemet alapvetoen koltsegvetesi
szempontok motivaltak: elmaradt a palyaztatas, a tozsdei ertekesites.

A szamvevok szerint a specialis honvedelmi-nemzetbiztonsagi
feladatokat is ellato ceg maganositasa soran tobb szabalytalansag
tortent.

A Nepszabadsag (Nagy Zoltan... 5.o.) parlamenti forrasbol ugy
ertesult, hogy lemondott a Garancia Biztosito vezerigazgatoi tiszterol
Nagy Zoltan, aki azonban tovabbra is ellatja a biztosito
igazgatosaganak elnoki teendoit. A lap informacioi szerint Nagy Zoltan
neve felmerult az Allami Szamvevoszek elnoki posztjara eselyesek
kozott. Nagy korabban a PM kozigazgatasi allamtitkarakent szerzett
gazdasagpolitikai es allamigazgatasi gyakorlatot. Az ujsag szerint
mostanra patthelyzet alakult ki az ASZ - immar honapok ota ures -
elnoki posztjanak betoltese korul, eddig ugyanis nem akadt olyan
jelolt, akinek eselye lenne arra, hogy valamennyi part tamogatasaval
lepjen Hagelmayer Istvan orokebe. A lap ugy tudja, hogy az MSZP Nyikos
Laszlo jelenlegi ASZ-alelnok, az SZDSZ pedig inkabb Kovacs Arpad
ASZ-igazgato elnokke valasztasat tartana jonak.

Kulpolitika

Gyakorlatilag eredmeny nelkul ert veget Horn Gyula es az RMDSZ
vezetoinek tegnapi konzultacioja. A kisebbsegi politikusok
megismeteltek a magyar-roman alapszerzodessel kapcsolatos
fenntartasaikat. Marko Bela szovetsegi elnok elismerte, hogy a
dokumentumnak vannak pozitiv elemei, a kollektiv jogok ertelmezesevel
szemben azonban a szervezet teljes egyet nem erteset fejezi ki. Ugy
velik, az ET 1201-es ajanlasat sulyosan csonkitja, hogy a
dokumentumhoz fuzott "labjegyzetben" azt nem tartjak ervenyesnek a
kollektiv jogokra. Hianyoljak azt is, hogy a szerzodesben nincs szo
az elkobzott egyhazi es kozossegi javak visszaadasarol, ami pedig
eredetileg szerepelt a tervezetben. Nem ertenek egyet azzal sem, hogy
a szerzodest a kozelgo romaniai elnok- es parlamenti valasztas elott
alairjak, gyenge garancianak tekintik ugyanis egy lekoszono kormany
hozzajarulasat. Tokes Laszlo szerint a magyar kormanynak kulso
kenyszerek hatasara lett ennyire surgos az alapszerzodes
veglegesitese, amellyel megszegte a juliusi magyar-magyar
csucstalalkozo zaronyilatkozata reven kialakult osszamagyar
konszenzust. A reformatus puspok ugy erzi, a magyar kulpolitika harom
fo celja kozott megbomlott az egyensuly, a hataron tuli kisebbsegek
tamogatasa hatterbe szorult, az europai integracio es a joszomszed
kapcsolatok mogott. Somogyi Ferenc allamtitkar hangsulyozta:

 [ a hazaarulas finomkodo leirasa: ]

 alapveto megkozelitesbeli kulonbsegek vannak a kormany es a romaniai
 magyarsag kozott az alapszerzodessel kapcsolatban.
 Budapest meggyozodese, hogy a jelenlegi helyzetben elerte a maximumot.[???]

Ezert a kormany a szovegegyeztetesi folyamatot befejezettnek tekinti,
s ezt Horn Gyula kozolte is az RMDSZ vezetoivel.

Teodor Melescanu roman kulugyminiszer tegnap biralta az RMDSZ-t, mert
a magyar kormanyt az alapszerzodes kisebbsegi cikelyeinek
megvaltoztatasara probalja ravenni (Magyar Hirlap: Sikertelen...
Melescanu... 1.,3.).

Hetfon osszegyultek az Orszaggyules rendkivuli ulesenek osszehivasahoz
szukseges alairasok 87 ellenzeki es fuggetlen kepviselo tamogatta,
hogy a parlament vitassa meg azt a javaslatot: a kormany ne irja ala
parlamenti felhatalmazas nelkul a magyar-roman alapszerzodest. Isepy
Tamas, a KDNP parlamenti frakciovezetoje ma adja at az iveket Gal
Zoltan hazelnoknek, s egyben keri, hogy a rendkivuli ulest augusztus
31-ere hivja ossze. Az FKGP Budapestre, a Kossuht terre hivja nema
gyertyagyujtasra mindazokat, akik szolidaritast vallalnak a hataron
tul elo magyarokkal es tiltakoznak a magyar-roman alapszerzodes
ellen. Az FKGP javasolja, hogy az ellenzeki partok allitsanak fel
intezobizottsagot a nemzeti gyasznap megszervezesere. Torgyan Jozsef
partelnok a felhivasban megallapitja: vegveszelybe kerult a magyarsag
a Karpat-medenceben, az MSZP-SZDSZ-kormany elarulta a hataron tul elo
honfitarsainkat (Magyar Hirlap: Nema... 3.o., Nepszabadsag:
Osszegyult... 3.o.).

Halara iteltek hetfon Cson Tu Hvan egykori del-koreai elnokot az
1979-es allamcsinyben valo reszveteleert. A szouli birosag szerint
Cson volt a puccs kiterveloje. Az allamcsiny idejen tabornoki rangban
szolgalo Csonnak az itelet szerint resze volt tobb magasrangu
katonatiszt elleni gyilkossagi kiserletben, s korrupcioban is
vetkesnek talaltatott. Utodjat, Ro Te Vu volt elnokot a birosag
hasonlo vadak alapjan 22 es fel evi bortonre itelte (Nepszava:
Halal... 1.o.).

ftp://ftp.ifi.uio.no/pub/pgp
